### REST Client Test File for Movie Collection API
### Make sure the server is running on http://localhost:3000

### 1. GET all movies (JSON)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies

### 2. GET default route (HTML page)
GET http://localhost:3000/

### 3. GET movie by ID (existing movie)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies/1

### 4. GET movie by ID (non-existent movie)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies/999

### 5. POST - Add a new movie
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Interstellar",
  "director": "Christopher Nolan",
  "year": 2014
}

### 6. POST - Add another movie
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Dark Knight",
  "director": "Christopher Nolan",
  "year": 2008
}

### 7. POST - Test validation (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Incomplete Movie"
}

### 8. GET all movies again (to verify new movies were added)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies

### 9. GET movies with query parameter - filter by year
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?year=2010

### 10. GET movies with query parameter - filter by director
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?director=Christopher Nolan

### 11. GET movies with query parameter - filter by title
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?title=Matrix

### 12. GET movies with multiple query parameters
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?year=2010&director=Christopher Nolan

### 13. PUT - Update an existing movie
PUT http://localhost:3000/movies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Inception (Updated)",
  "year": 2010
}

### 14. PUT - Update movie with all fields
PUT http://localhost:3000/movies/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Matrix Reloaded",
  "director": "The Wachowskis",
  "year": 2003
}

### 15. PUT - Test validation (invalid year)
PUT http://localhost:3000/movies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "year": 1800
}

### 16. PUT - Test 404 (non-existent movie)
PUT http://localhost:3000/movies/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Non-existent Movie"
}

### 17. DELETE - Delete a movie
DELETE http://localhost:3000/movies/3

### 18. DELETE - Test 404 (non-existent movie)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/movies/999

### 19. GET all movies after deletion
GET http://localhost:3000/movies

### 20. Test catch-all route (undefined route)
GET http://localhost:3000/undefined-route

